High durability means data placed in the cloud would not be loosed
Availability is how quickly one can access their data
High Availability provides fast and reliable access to the data store in the cloud.
Scalability allows aplications runnning in ones' environment to always meet demand seamlesly by adding or removing resources neccessary to maintain steady state and fast response time.

3 types of scaling
Vertical Scaling aka scaling up: is adding more capacity like disk, CPU to the server,
Horizontal scaling or scaling out: is addingmore servers to the server being used
Diagonal scaling: is the combination of both
